subject: Attn: Fund Beneficiary.
body:
Attn: Fund Beneficiary.
You have a Pending Transfer Value of USD10.5M in your name, and are
awaiting for a clearance Certificate from  (FinCEN) before we can
authorize the transfer  into your account.
The FBI need's copy of your  Fund Identification Record Certificate
of the transfer. You should get back to us if you don't  have  this
certificate for us to direct you where you can get one for further
release of your fund into your account.
Mr. Gareth Reese
FOR: Christopher A. Wray
FBI Director

subject: Re:   Attn: Fund Beneficiary.
body:
Hello Mr. Gareth Reese,

Thank you for reaching out to me about this pending transfer. I must admit, I'm a bit surprised as I wasn't expecting any transfers. Could you please provide more details about this? Where is the transfer coming from and why does it require clearance?

I don't have a Fund Record of the transfer at the moment. Could you kindly guide me on how to obtain one? 

Looking forward to your guidance.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Jeff
